, https://github.com/apache/hive/pull/32, this case was incomplete and was recently improved to include other join filters (see "dbHasJoinCastBug" there). However, we didn't realize postgres also has this bug, so it needs to be added to the list.
With the full case filter it should not try to cast non-numerics unless they are actually stored in the numeric column. Can you check where "DEFAULT_BINSRC" value is coming from?]